Package com.fasterxml.clustermate.client.operation

Package that contains abstractions used for handling of logical operations that may consist of multiple physical (HTTP) calls.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    OperationResult<T extends OperationResult<T>>
    Class used for returning information about operation success (or lack thereof).
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DeleteOperationResult  
    GetOperationResult<T>
    OperationResult subtype used with GET operations, adds actual result (of type T which is type of GetContentProcessor passed to call).
    HeadOperationResult  
    ListOperationResult<T>
    Result value produced by StoreEntryLister, contains information about success of individual call, as well as sequence of listed entries in case of successful call.
    OperationConfig  
    OperationResultImpl<T extends OperationResultImpl<T>>
    Intermediate base class to simplify actual result implementations.
    PutOperationResult  
    ReadOperationResult<T extends ReadOperationResult<T>>
    Intermediate base class for read operations (GET, HEAD, List).
    StoreEntryLister<K extends EntryKey,T>
    Value class that is used as result type for content list operation.
